| **Payload size risk** | Limited JSON/URL body to 1MB |
| **No error handling** | Added try-catch and global error handler |
| **No logging** | Added morgan for request logging |
| **Sensitive data exposure** | Added pagination to limit user data returned |
| **Missing 404 handling** | Added proper 404 handler |
